title: AVTECH Room Alert 3S: Sensor Humidity
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/avtech
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the internal humidity
 and the humidity of sensors connected to
 a AVTECH Room Alert 3S device.
 Upper and lower levels can be configured
 via the _Humidity levels_ ruleset.

item:
 "Humidity Sensor" if the connected sensor is a humidity sensor.

discovery:
 One service is created if the sensor emits humidity data.
